thread.title: Phyl Westhorpe
thread.title_full: Temple & Webster reviewed by Phyl Westhorpe

author: Phyl Westhorpe
title: Phyl Westhorpe
text: We ordered Chantal chairs of which one arrived damaged and we contacted the company and the staff who took our call were first class we were so impressed with the level of service and help they gave us and our chair was replaced as soon as available which was approximately 2 week's.
